subject: Login Failure
body: User unable to log in with correct credentials.

subject: Password Reset
body: Requested password reset link not working.

subject: Account Locked
body: Customer's account was locked after multiple failed login attempts.

subject: Refund Request
body: Customer is requesting a refund for a duplicate charge.

subject: App Crash
body: Mobile app crashes when trying to upload a file.

subject: Feature Request
body: Customer suggests adding dark mode to the dashboard.

subject: Security Concern
body: Customer suspects unauthorized access to their account.

subject: Payment Failure
body: Customer's payment did not go through despite sufficient funds.

subject: Slow Performance
body: Dashboard takes too long to load during peak hours.
